description: This file is a C header defining the API for the Dslh Wmp Database object, including function prototypes for creating, removing, enrolling objects, and initializing the database, as well as a factory function for creating the database.

methods.name: DslhCreateWmpDatabase
methods.description: Creates a new Wmp Database instance with specified container, owner, and reserved contexts.

methods.name: DslhWmpdoCreate
methods.description: Creates a new Wmp Database object with specified container, owner, and reserved contexts.

methods.name: DslhWmpdoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls the necessary objects into the Wmp Database.
